'''CITV'''是[[英國|英國]]的一個電視頻道，播出兒童收看的電視節目，由[[獨立電視公司|獨立電視公司]]所有，播出時間是每天早上六點至晚上九點，和CBBC相同<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.reddit.com/r/BritishTV/comments/47c7zf/citv_extend_their_broadcast_hours_to_9pm_ahead_of/|title=CITV extend their broadcast hours to 9pm ahead of CBBC doing the same after BBC3 closure. • /r/BritishTV|website=reddit|access-date=2016-03-15|archive-date=2016-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160301155424/https://www.reddit.com/r/BritishTV/comments/47c7zf/citv_extend_their_broadcast_hours_to_9pm_ahead_of|dead-url=no}}</ref>。CITV也是[[獨立電視台_(英國)|獨立電視台]]在週末兒童節目時段的節目名稱<ref name="interim">{{cite web|url=http://www.investis.com/itv/downloads/interim2005.pdf|title=ITV Interim Results - 6 months to 2005-06-30|accessdate=14 January 2007|format=PDF|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20061016083717/http://www.investis.com/itv/downloads/interim2005.pdf|archivedate=2006-10-16|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。

